024-amsterdam-buy-tickets-3599673">安排了许多夏季欧洲音乐节</a>，包括 Way Out West、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oya-festival-2024-adds-queens-of-the-stone-age-the-smile-the-national-and-more-3553501">Øya</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flow-festival-announces-pulp-pj-harvey-the-smile-fred-again-and-more-for-stacked-2024-line-up-3547974">Flow Festival</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jarvis-cocker-teases-more-pulp-shows-and-discusses-new-project-biophobia-i-used-to-be-scared-of-nature-3595600">在今年 3 月接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jarvis-cocker">贾维斯·科克 (Jarvis Cocker)</a>证实，该乐队的巡演计划将延长至 2025 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-add-more-shows-to-first-north-america-tour-in-over-a-decade-3605361">。此后，他们宣布将于今年秋季举行十多年来的首次北美巡演</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-debut-new-song-background-noise-live-in-mexico-3542753">Pulp 于 12 月在墨西哥的一场演出中首次推出了新歌“Background Noise</a> ”。鼓手 Nick Banks <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulps-nick-banks-on-his-new-memoir-the-bands-future-and-the-joke-of-britpop-3509203">最近也向 NME 暗示，乐队可能会推出更多新材料</a>，但对很快就会有新音乐并不确定。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-play-bar-italia-for-first-time-in-12-years-3768123">Watch Pulp 的后剧“Bar Italia”12 年来首次</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
