 《加勒比海盗》演员塔马约·佩里被鲨鱼咬死https://www.nme.com/news/film/pirates-of-the-caribbean-actor-tamayo-perry-killed-by-shark-3768148?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pirates-of-the-caribbean-演员塔马约·佩里被鲨鱼杀死Alex BerryMon, 24 Jun 2024 11:05:29 +0000 Film NewsNews.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3768148 <p><img width="1443" height="916" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="塔马约·佩里" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2.jpg 1443w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1443px) 100vw, 1443px" /></p><p>该演员在欧胡岛冲浪时遭到袭击</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/pirates-of-the-caribbean-actor-tamayo-perry-killed-by-shark-3768148">《加勒比海盗》演员塔马约·佩里被鲨鱼咬死的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1443" height="916" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="塔马约·佩里" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2.jpg 1443w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1443px) 100vw, 1443px" /></p><p>塔马约·佩里 (Tamayo Perry) 是一名冲浪教练和演员，因在<em>《加勒比海盗：惊涛怪浪》</em>中扮演的角色而闻名，他因鲨鱼袭击而死亡。</p><p> 49 岁的佩里在夏威夷欧胡岛冲浪时遭到鲨鱼袭击，随后被一艘摩托艇带到了岸边。</p><p>檀香山紧急服务部门在新闻发布会上证实了他于周日下午（6 月 23 日）去世的消息。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cd1117lwlxyo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em></a>报道，当地时间下午 1 点左右，紧急服务人员抵达欧胡岛北部的 Malaekahana 海滩，接到报警电话称一名男子身上有类似鲨鱼咬伤的伤口。佩里被带到岸上后被医护人员当场宣布死亡。</p><p>檀香山海洋安全局代理局长库尔特·拉格 (Kurt Lager) 称佩里为“一位深受所有人喜爱的救生员”，并表示他在欧胡岛北岸很有名。</p><p> “塔马约的个性很有感染力，人们爱他，但他更爱其他人，”他分享道。</p><p> “我们向塔马约的家人表示哀悼。” </p><figure id="attachment_3768154" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768154" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768154" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean.jpg" alt="塔马约·佩里" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tamayo-Perry-pirates-of-the-Caribbean-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768154" class="wp-caption-text">塔马约·佩里，2019 年 1 月 2 日。图片来源：Getty/BRIAN BIELMANN/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>市长里克·布兰贾迪在新闻发布会上表示：“塔马约是一位传奇的水手，备受尊敬，他在这里长大，也是我们海洋安全团队的优秀成员。”</p><p>他称佩里的去世是“悲惨的损失”。</p><p>佩里在 2011 年上映的<em>《加勒比海盗》</em>系列第四部电影中扮演了一名海盗，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-depp">约翰尼·德普</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/penelope-cruz">佩内洛普·克鲁兹</a>和杰弗里·拉什合作。</p><p>佩里还曾在 2002 年的体育浪漫电影<em>《Blue Crush》</em>中出演过角色，在<em>《夏威夷五比零》</em>中露面，并在<em>《迷失》</em>和<em>《查理的天使：全速前进》</em>中扮演角色。</p><p>佩里和他的妻子艾米莉亚建立了<a href="https://www.oahusurfingexperience.com/instructors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">欧胡岛冲浪体验</a>中心，这是一所位于北岸的冲浪学校，“致力于为您提供大多数大型冲浪学校无法提供的安全、有教育意义和纯粹愉快的体验。”</p><p>在他们的网站上，佩里描述了他令人印象深刻的冲浪经验和知识，以及他的表演。他在个人简介中总结道：“当我不演戏时，我仍然很有个性，所以总是有很多乐趣。”</p><p>在艾米莉亚的简历中，她这样描述她的丈夫：“塔马约多年来在我心中根深蒂固的大量海洋知识是无价的。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/pirates-of-the-caribbean-actor-tamayo-perry-killed-by-shark-3768148">《加勒比海盗》演员塔马约·佩里被鲨鱼咬死的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
